    "description": "Johnson & Johnson India Consulting Pvt Ltd is actively seeking a talented and motivated Senior Doctor to join our dynamic team in Bhopal. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Johnson & Johnson India Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nJohnson & Johnson India Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor patient progress and adjust treatment plans accordingly\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Collaborate with pharmaceutical representatives and medical suppliers\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in HIPAA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Telemedicine\n• Proficiency in EMR/EHR\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in Clinical Documentation\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Johnson & Johnson India Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
